plying this procedure to two experimental data sets gives values of the\nbeneficial mutation rate within the range of previous measurements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 20 Oct 2012 22:58:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Dec 2012 18:51:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 19 Dec 2012 18:58:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-12-20"}
