mentation issues for GPU acceleration are\nbriefly discussed, and the performance of the algorithm is tested for a number\nof hardware configurations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 21 Oct 2012 01:23:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
